  "detailed_description": "<strong>Before the Echo</strong> combines elements of both rhythm and role-playing games to create an entirely unique experience. Join Ky on his ascent of a mysterious Tower, guided onward by a mysterious girl named Naia. Encounter deadly monsters and ridiculous characters, and discover the grand scheme behind Ky's mysterious imprisonment...that is, if you can survive the journey.<br><br>\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2> \t\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fully voice-acted, 10+ hour story mode<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>With music by Ronald Jenkees and Michael Wade Hamilton<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>Deep item synthesis and spell customization mechanics provide a full RPG experience<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>Full integration of Steam achievements and cloud saves<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t</li></ul>",
